🏠 OUR FAMILY CALENDAR APP 📅
================================

Hey there! Welcome to our super cool Family Calendar! 🎉

WHAT IS THIS? 🤔
----------------
You know how sometimes Dad forgets about your soccer practice, 
or Mom asks "What should we have for dinner?" like 100 times?

Well, this app fixes ALL of that! It's like a magic board where 
our whole family can see:
  ✓ What's happening each day
  ✓ What yummy food we're eating
  ✓ What groceries we need to buy

WHAT CAN YOU DO? 🎮
-------------------

📅 THE CALENDAR
   - See everyone's stuff on one calendar
   - Dad's meetings = BLUE
   - Mom's stuff = RED  
   - Your activities = GREEN
   - Click on any day to add something new!

🍽️ MEAL PLANNER
   - Pick what we eat for:
     🌅 Breakfast (morning food!)
     🌤️ Lunch (noon munchies!)
     🍪 Snack (yay snacks!)
     🌙 Dinner (family time food!)
   - No more "I don't know what to eat" 

🛒 GROCERY LIST
   - The app makes a shopping list FROM the meals!
   - Check off items at the store
   - Never forget the good snacks again!

HOW TO START IT? 🚀
-------------------
1. Ask a grown-up to open the terminal (the black screen with typing)
2. Type: npm install (this downloads helper stuff - like getting ingredients)
3. Type: npm run dev (this turns on the app!)
4. Go to: http://localhost:3000 in your browser
5. BOOM! You're in! 💥

WHO'S IN OUR FAMILY? 👨‍👩‍👧
--------------------------
Right now the app has:
  🔵 Parent 1
  🔴 Parent 2  
  🟢 Child (that's YOU!)

(A grown-up can change the names in the code!)

THE COOL PART 🌟
----------------
If we set up something called "Firebase" (it's free!), 
EVERYONE in the family can see the same calendar from 
their own phone or computer. Like magic! ✨

Without Firebase, it only works on one device - still cool though!

HAVE FUN! 🎈
------------
Now go plan some awesome family activities and yummy meals!

